read each file for copyright or license.
While I (andyh) authored most of these some other folk may have helped and someone might have added files found on the web.


If you have compilation difficulties such as missing pieces please check github 980f/safely/cppext for an alternate version.
The safely lib is written for systems with an OS, the ezcpp for microcontrollers, but everything in cppext should be able to function on a microcontroller, they are just not optimized for them.
